13:31.835 --> 13:33.717
Now, that's true.

13:34.198 --> 13:36.240
I don't think that's what John is up to.

13:38.322 --> 13:38.802
I think

13:39.330 --> 13:44.337
John would say, faith is action.

13:44.397 --> 13:47.501
It doesn't just bring about action.

13:50.425 --> 13:52.168
That's where I'm starting.

13:54.110 --> 13:55.452
I'm going to check that out.

13:56.734 --> 13:59.378
