15:39.630 --> 15:40.751
What's going on in me?

15:41.913 --> 15:43.254
This is a divine miracle.

15:43.595 --> 15:44.075
What is it?

15:44.636 --> 15:45.797
How do I experience it?

15:47.259 --> 15:50.342
So to answer that question, what is the acting of faith?

15:51.103 --> 15:55.969
Let's go first to John chapter one, verses 11 to 13.

15:56.389 --> 15:57.450
Very familiar text.

15:57.851 --> 16:00.594
