16:10.018 --> 16:14.465
Jesus came to His own and His own people did not receive Him.

16:16.128 --> 16:26.546
But to all who did receive Him, who believed in His name, I've noticed, you call that a positive in grammar.

16:28.322 --> 16:32.786
to all who did receive him, comma, who believed in his name.

